Title : List of museums in Andalusia
Text : This is a '''list of museums in Andalusia'''. According to the Ministry of Culture, there are 186 museums in [[Andalusia]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcu.es/estadisticas/MC/EM/2012/Index2012.html |title=Estadística de Museos y Colecciones Museográficas 2012 |author= |date=February 2014 |publisher=Ministry of Culture |accessdate=2014-04-29 |language=Spanish |trans-title=2012 Statistics of Museums and Collections |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429211116/http://www.mcu.es/estadisticas/MC/EM/2012/Index2012.html |archive-date=2014-04-29 |df= }}</ref>

